{"id": "1454104712545566872", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "905807477520609321", "author_name": "shangxianyue_sp", "author_bot": false, "content": "其实我还有一些别的想法\n现在都有融灾禁区了\n其实还可以“借鉴”一下粥的塔防玩法\n搞个融灾防线\n反正素材都现成的\n唤醒体，融蚀体都有\n地图就选弥萨格，港口，勒姆瓦希，黑池", "timestamp": "2025-12-26T13:32:59.430000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
